name: IV. TERRA (EARTH)
description:
Work linked to the power of the earth through the triad that represents the materialization of us. The earth nourishes and sustains the whole so that life can manifest itself in full harmony, it provides food for the soul. In gratitude to her for providing us with life, we open ourselves to understanding the symbiosis between human and earth, felt from within in a germinating grain, manifesting all its wisdom in its fractals, awakening its spirit and integrating itself with the whole .

Year: 2020 | Technique: Digital art made in ProCreate

This artwork is from a limited edition of 20 prints
